OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPontins discriminated      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fagainst Irish Travellers - 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FEHRC                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Holiday park operator Pontins has      
OL,6, apologised after being issued a legal  
OL,7, notice for "shocking" discrimination   
OL,8, towards Irish Travellers.              
OL,10,FThe Equality and Human Rights          
OL,11,FCommission (EHRC) found Pontins had    
OL,12,Fcreated a list of common Irish surnames
OL,13,Flabelled as "undesirable guests".      
OL,15,FIt said staff were told to decline or  
OL,16,Fcancel bookings made under those names 
OL,17,For by people with Irish accents.       
OL,19,FPontins said the incidents in the      
OL,20,Freport were historic.                  
